{
  "text": "We have previously reported that three distinct fibroblast populations can be isolated from P2 dermis. DP cells from GAA follicles are CD133 \u00fe Sox2 \u00fe , whereas DP cells from ZZ follicles are CD133 \u00fe Sox2\u00c0 and non-DP cells are CD133\u00c0Sox2\u00c0 [CITATION_1] . In skin reconstitution assays, Sox2 \u00fe cells are required for the formation of GAA follicles and CD133\u00c0 cells do not induce hair follicle formation [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
